title: Lindsay Lohan is mad that Amanda Bynes isn't in jail
text:
As you should know all too well, Lindsay, it takes several run-ins with the law before the Los Angeles Police Department actually does anything to famous people.
Because of the notoriously lax way that the LAPD treats celebrity scofflaws, Bynes has a lot of catching up to do before she has to spend five hours of a 30-day sentence in jail, only to bereleased due to “overcrowding.”
 Lindsay Lohan
